'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2870] on 12 October 2000 at 5:26:28 pm'!"Change Set:		FlushCacheDate:			12 October 2000Author:			Andreas RaabPer Ian's suggestion: Flush the old compiled method when when replacing it."!!MethodDictionary methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 10/12/2000 17:25'!at: key put: value	"Set the value at key to be value."	| index |	index _ self findElementOrNil: key.	(self basicAt: index) == nil		ifTrue: 			[tally _ tally + 1.			self basicAt: index put: key]		ifFalse:			[(array at: index) flushCache].	array at: index put: value.	self fullCheck.	^ value! !